title: ALL Project Camelot Interviews up to May 2008 [UFO ET 2012]
description:
ProjectCamelot.org is a website run by Kerry Cassidy and Bill Ryan under the name Project Camelot. The website serves to host testimonial on-record interviews with whistle blowers revealing insider information about classified projects, UFO/alien contact and earth changes.

All video interviews are available individually from www.projectcamelot.org and Google Video. This torrent contains ALL of the MOV & MP4 format interviews from May 2006 to May 2008, including extra material such as audio messages from Leo Zagami, The Gore Report recording, and the theme song \\\\\\\"Jaguar\\\\\\\". These files can be played with Quicktime Player or VNC. This torrent was created because the MOV/MP4 files are higher quality than the WMV files of other torrents.

The information discussed in these interviews is not for the faint hearted or closed minded. At the very least, treat this as great sci-fi.

Rejoice in the love and light, and go forth in the power of the one Creator.
Enjoy!
